                    <div class="card-overlay flex flex-col justify-between pt-10 px-10 pb-10 hidden">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>Custom Comes Standard</h3>
                            <p>Off-the-shelf solutions can only go so far, often falling short of industry-specific needs. Our mantra, <em>Custom Comes Standard</em>, empowers manufacturers to break through constraints, enhance efficiency, and achieve precision.</p>
                            <p>In a world where innovation and optimization are crucial, custom tools elevate manufacturing to new heights, delivering tailor-made solutions for industry excellence.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <button class="btn white-outline"><a href="/custom-quote">Design Your Tool <i class="fa-solid fa-pencil ms-3"></i> </a></button>
