                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content flex flex-col">
                        <h3>Custom Tools</h3>
                        <p>Precision crafted, tailored for your needs.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="services-card sales-rep">
                    <div class="card-overlay flex flex-col justify-between pt-10 px-10 pb-10 hidden">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>Get The Help You Need</h3>
                            <p>Our sales team are experts in helping you find the tools you need for your application. Not sure what you need? Our team can help you find solutions that match your goals.</p>
                            <p>Use our sales map to find which representative works with customers in your area.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <button class="btn white-outline"><a href="/sales-team-map/">Find Your Rep <i class="fa-solid fa-user ms-3"></i> </a></button>
