                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3 class="title">Find a Sales Rep</h3>
                        <p>Connect with a member of our team.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full xl:w-6/12 px-4 md:px-10 lg:pt-28">
                <div class="services-card reconditioning ">
                    <div class="card-overlay flex flex-col justify-between pt-10 px-10 pb-10 hidden">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>Why Regrind?</h3>
                            <p>Regrinding old tools holds a pivotal role in sustainable manufacturing practices. It's not just about extending the lifespan of tools; it's a testament to resourcefulness and cost-effectiveness.</p>
                            <p> In an era where sustainability and efficiency are paramount, regrinding old tools is both a practical necessity and a responsible choice.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <button class="btn white-outline"><a href="/tool-reconditioning">Regrind Your Tool <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right ms-3"></i> </a></button>
