                <div class="services-card industries">
                    <div class="card-overlay flex flex-col justify-between pt-10 px-10 pb-10 hidden">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>Engineered for Every Industry</h3>
                            <p>GWS cutting tools are utilized across a wide array of industries, showcasing versatility and precision. From automotive to medical to aerospace, our tools are designed to meet the diverse needs of various sectors.</p>
                            <p>Discover how our cutting-edge tools are transforming industries by delivering exceptional performance and reliability.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <button class="btn white-outline"><a href="/industries">See All Industries <i class="fa-solid fa-truck-plane ms-3"></i> </a></button>
                        </div>
                        
